• Greater China revenue increased 23%

China  business turned to profit for two consecutive quarters with improved business structure and cost reduction measures \- Strengthened market responsiveness and growth momentum through new product launches, including  Sulwhasoo(renewed ‘Essential Duo’), Laneige(‘Glaze Craze Tinted Lip Serum,’ ‘Lip GlowyBalm’), and Ryo (‘Hair Strength  Aroma Perfume Shampoo Hangzhou Edition,’ ‘CICA Scalp Calming Shampoo’)

\- \[APAC\] Sulwhasooincreased customer purchase with its global campaign (‘First Care Activating Serum’), Laneige enhanced brand attractiveness and drove sales growth for its ‘Bouncy and Firm’ line through collaborative  marketing and pop-up event with a local brand, and emerging brands (Aestura/Hera/Illiyoon) expanded brand  presence in both online and offline channels 

\- \[Japan\] Enhanced brand appeal of Laneige(‘Neo Cushion Mewy’, ‘Gel Cream Skin’) and Aestura(‘Theracne365’)  through innovative products and achieved strong sales growth for major brands (Laneige/Aestura/Primera/Hera)  via co-marketing activities with major multi-brand shop retailers (@cosme Tokyo Cushion Festa, Loft pop-up store)
